{"tid":27010,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"吾系甘牙","createTime":"2016-12-07T05:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T05:57:49.000Z","uid":57211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00cdeabc762b897e07d087c5abd7d92e4fb2ea4d","tid":27010,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:17:33.000Z","msg":"真係見到就好撚燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有咩碎 碎乜撚野碎 幾廿歲人「歲」字都唔識寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n挽乜撚野挽 明明「玩」同「挽」都唔撚岩音<br />\n番屋企挽鞋啦屌<br />\n<br />\n天日 究竟咩係天日 係天定係日 打字打到你好似啲脷登咁<br />\n<br />\nBtw「尐」字係幾時出現 唔知幾時開始好多mk 同 小朋友用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0359fb8d1b37723499d9f133868995de9f62c5cb","tid":27010,"uid":57312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"93f9f433dc2972cb8e526f6f7b1642b6f56ddbb5","tid":27010,"uid":56488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"尐 點讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15b0fe98beb19e442182224908ab04cd8440737","tid":27010,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg&h=316857f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說文解字話係 啲 嘅本字"},{"pid":"f9775b2234e558b0017eeb3a3ec423b113d168bf","tid":27010,"uid":48729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg&h=316857f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說文解字話係 啲 嘅本字</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係呀。<br />\n尐讀節，唔係啲嘅本字。"},{"pid":"22e109c19ac3c2301b1cfd180502ca57ff7f9267","tid":27010,"uid":57211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:57:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F133147_ab4d6f4d991391a8de57802add9ff219.jpg&h=316857f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說文解字話係 啲 嘅本字</blockquote><br />\n唔撚係呀。<br />\n尐讀節，唔係啲嘅本字。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近年有人將「尐」呢個生僻字，講成係「啲」嘅本字或正字，原因係「尐」解作少，同「啲」（解作一點、一些）有相似嘅地方，更有專欄作家同報章評論員將佢誤傳。「啲」嘅讀音係di1，但「尐」嘅讀音係zit3，尐嘅反切係「子列切」，反切上字取聲母(子-&gt;zi-&gt;z)，下字取韻母(列-&gt;lit-&gt;it)，切出嚟嘅音就係zit，讀音都唔啱，所以無可能係本字或正字。而且意思唔係相同，例如「多啲」（多一點），如果寫成「多尐」就會變成（多少），意思已經唔同咗。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/尐\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh-yue.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%B0%90&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=2f1fec12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh-yue.wikipedia.org/wiki/尐</a><br />\n<br />\n原來佢解少 但係唔讀啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}